    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/3141ff9f27722709a0b85364aa791c0c.webp?t=1770110747\" width=643 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目前仅提供英文版！但我们希望让更多玩家有机会发现它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/ace86e43809efe850764ab910caee3a0.webp?t=1770110747\" width=652 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/d57195d89f00c9789cf77a24be408681.poster.avif?t=1770110747\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/d57195d89f00c9789cf77a24be408681.webm?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/d57195d89f00c9789cf77a24be408681.mp4?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/01c43f08a24637a32ff8e06d50259369.webp?t=1770110747\" width=644 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度个人化的角色扮演体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择塑造的不仅仅是故事——它们铸就了塞勒姆的身份认同。当忠诚与邪恶政权下的禁忌之爱发生冲突时，每个决定都会将你更深地拉入他的内心斗争。随着多个独特结局等待被发现，你的塞勒姆可能成为英雄、反派，或者更加复杂的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/ace86e43809efe850764ab910caee3a0.webp?t=1770110747\" width=652 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/16c37538d909cdaf026e18b727fa2f5d.poster.avif?t=1770110747\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/16c37538d909cdaf026e18b727fa2f5d.webm?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/16c37538d909cdaf026e18b727fa2f5d.mp4?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/3141ff9f27722709a0b85364aa791c0c.webp?t=1770110747\" width=643 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态角色关系</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色们会记住你的行为，并随着你的选择而演变。背叛一个朋友，他们再也不会用同样的眼光看你。展现意想不到的善意，敌人可能会成为盟友。你的人际关系在每次游玩中都会发生变化，每次都创造出真正个性化的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/01c43f08a24637a32ff8e06d50259369.webp?t=1770110747\" width=644 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/22ae5bf862168a323ab81381e34206c5.poster.avif?t=1770110747\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/22ae5bf862168a323ab81381e34206c5.webm?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/22ae5bf862168a323ab81381e34206c5.mp4?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/ace86e43809efe850764ab910caee3a0.webp?t=1770110747\" width=652 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>分秒必争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当时钟开始滴答作响时，你的本能会揭示你的真实面目。面对紧张时刻，犹豫意味着死亡，而瞬间的选择决定着谁生谁死。对于喜爱充满真实后果的情感丰富叙事的玩家，Rottenroots带来了真正道德困境的肾上腺素冲击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/3141ff9f27722709a0b85364aa791c0c.webp?t=1770110747\" width=643 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/299a600894c9c6daa1156b6e44359965.poster.avif?t=1770110747\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/299a600894c9c6daa1156b6e44359965.webm?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/299a600894c9c6daa1156b6e44359965.mp4?t=1770110747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/01c43f08a24637a32ff8e06d50259369.webp?t=1770110747\" width=644 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>令人着迷的美丽反乌托邦</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个被邪恶腐蚀的太阳朋克世界中，乌托邦与噩梦之间的界限随着时间的推移而日渐模糊。当塞勒姆在一个顺从意味着生存的社会中穿行时，每一个隐藏的秘密都是另一条向更深处生长的根须。体验一个科技与自然交融的世界，抵抗在意想不到的地方绽放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/ace86e43809efe850764ab910caee3a0.webp?t=1770110747\" width=652 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为什么你会爱上Rottenroots</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验个性系统，你的选择塑造塞勒姆的性格特征，在每次游玩中解锁独特的对话选项和故事路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现多种结局，从令人心碎的悲剧到苦乐参半的胜利，每一个都反映了你道德选择的高潮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在Laura Meggers（</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即添加到愿望单！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177730/extras/3141ff9f27722709a0b85364aa791c0c.webp?t=1770110747\" width=643 height=46 /></span></p>",
